<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-40-0211 </DOCNO><TEXT>EEC policy developments over the last five years are briefly reviewed.An appraisal of the emission standards in the EEC Luxemburg 1985 Agreementand possible second step standards for the under 1.4 litre car is givenin the light of the desired EEC-US '83 equivalency. A second importantaspect is the representation of European driving conditions in a testcycle to be developed during 1987. Existing proposals are evaluated.</TEXT></DOC>